OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain at times, mainly
OL,7,Facross the Pennines. Drier to the east
OL,8,Fof the Pennines with occasional cloud
OL,9,Fbreaks. Breezy and mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,12,Frain across the Pennines becoming
OL,13,Fheavier and more persistent through
OL,14,FThursday, before easing for a time in
OL,15,Fthe evening. Drier in the east. Rather
OL,16,Fwindy, mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
