OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday,
OL,6,Frain some heavy, clearing later.
OL,7,FOccasionally strong winds. Saturday
OL,8,Fmostly dry, some bright spells and
OL,9,Flighter winds. Sunday, rain heavy
OL,10,Facross the Pennines, drier in east.
OL,11,FWindy but mild.
